            <description><![CDATA[
<h2>DynamicStage 3.0.0</h2>
<p>Rebrand from boring.notch with new features:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Dedicated guitar button</strong> – Single-click: search Ultimate Guitar; double-click: play from tab in Apple Music</li>
    <li><strong>Shortcuts</strong> – ⌥⌘T (search), ⌥⌘P (play from tab)</li>
    <li><strong>Notch-anchored settings</strong> – Popover instead of separate window</li>
    <li><strong>Notification cards</strong> – Calendar, Reminders, Messages, Mail in the notch</li>
    <li><strong>New app icon</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://github.com/Tide-Trends/boring.notch/releases">View all releases</a></p>
